{"tid":747171,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插地求救] 有冇人用鼻呼吸/打側瞓都會扯鼻鼾？","createTime":"2018-07-18T07:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T16:34:47.000Z","uid":121831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d126180ff9c0f73656d8c2fb49d7e9fea6095b","tid":747171,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見好多都話係口呼吸先有鼻鼾<br />\n但我係用鼻呼吸都有<br />\n同埋就算打側瞓都照扯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係個鼻有事<br />\n睇政府門診轉介係咪要等好耐？<br />\n就咁去睇出面私人嘅耳鼻喉科要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲都有經驗可以分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72cb072d02149745955fff0689f7e7c6cc1fe88","tid":747171,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f499cf0e2081b9ad4857a6e03d2c125e3a38a2","tid":747171,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5c24e9a1bff0ff1c97e85eabb89798e6f6c088","tid":747171,"uid":41937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"用左某d訓教果陣錄扯鼻寒的app 原本扯鼻寒佔左成個訓教時間20% 之後轉左個貴少少的記憶枕頭 之後 得返2-5% <br />\n枕頭可能都係一個因素搞到扯鼻寒"},{"pid":"c59265eea9ae70dc74c4f91ee1c5216e86a86076","tid":747171,"uid":41937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be5c24e9a1bff0ff1c97e85eabb89798e6f6c088","tid":747171,"uid":41937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"用左某d訓教果陣錄扯鼻寒的app 原本扯鼻寒佔左成個訓教時間20% 之後轉左個貴少少的記憶枕頭 之後 得返2-5% <br />\n枕頭可能都係一個因素搞到扯鼻寒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"以前未轉枕頭果陣試過用日本出果d貼住個口唔比佢訓教果陣張開 聲稱咁就可以止到鼻寒 但都冇咩用 <br />\n<br />\n好多時訓教果陣 如果剩係用鼻呼吸 出現呼吸唔暢順果陣就自然會張口個口幫助呼吸 <br />\n<br />\n果陣訓教用張貼紙 訓醒唔見左 係地下搵返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲以為自己食左"},{"pid":"bc2712cc468d771d025e196c4e902df2468668fd","tid":747171,"uid":159186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:53:03.000Z","msg":"習慣用口<br />\n訓個時用口試下  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過訓着左有時都係變返鼻呼吸"},{"pid":"f9a3e08065132cb2138ef19637c6d9c0061c71de","tid":747171,"uid":48611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be5c24e9a1bff0ff1c97e85eabb89798e6f6c088","tid":747171,"uid":41937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"用左某d訓教果陣錄扯鼻寒的app 原本扯鼻寒佔左成個訓教時間20% 之後轉左個貴少少的記憶枕頭 之後 得返2-5% <br />\n枕頭可能都係一個因素搞到扯鼻寒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"咩app"},{"pid":"40bed24a320553ffd332bd0014faaa7734b21de5","tid":747171,"uid":127955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"用左呼吸機冇曬鼻鼾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37d597efb25c14c9d28b4d9d7d72b663ee75033","tid":747171,"uid":41937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9a3e08065132cb2138ef19637c6d9c0061c71de","tid":747171,"uid":48611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be5c24e9a1bff0ff1c97e85eabb89798e6f6c088","tid":747171,"uid":41937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"用左某d訓教果陣錄扯鼻寒的app 原本扯鼻寒佔左成個訓教時間20% 之後轉左個貴少少的記憶枕頭 之後 得返2-5% <br />\n枕頭可能都係一個因素搞到扯鼻寒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"咩app"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"Snorelap 其實係app store打個snore 字就有一堆"},{"pid":"0dcd3cb3753adfc0cb6220775893b433ba112150","tid":747171,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be5c24e9a1bff0ff1c97e85eabb89798e6f6c088","tid":747171,"uid":41937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"用左某d訓教果陣錄扯鼻寒的app 原本扯鼻寒佔左成個訓教時間20% 之後轉左個貴少少的記憶枕頭 之後 得返2-5% <br />\n枕頭可能都係一個因素搞到扯鼻寒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講吓買咩牌子枕頭<br />\n我都有用app記錄<br />\n幾日都係八十幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇諗過自己鼻鼾聲咁勁，以前不嬲都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都幾肯定自己係冇用口呼吸<br />\n因為我有用呼吸帶（箍住成個頭唔俾口擘大）<br />\n同埋我係<strong>側瞓</strong>都照有鼻鼾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146bceb74faa0efcfc0d88a23361fe9a16981b1a","tid":747171,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40bed24a320553ffd332bd0014faaa7734b21de5","tid":747171,"uid":127955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"用左呼吸機冇曬鼻鼾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:03:21.000Z","msg":"但我上網睇係治標唔治本<br />\n同埋去旅行咪好麻煩<br />\n要帶多部機去"},{"pid":"958bb72dd568197025cb507be4d1ac74a79674ed","tid":747171,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445c0d8aa11c0f618d5bb15d17eaa32c67f3d8ec","tid":747171,"uid":146066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:07:37.000Z","msg":"睡眠窒息症？"},{"pid":"c91df9097aeb87fef04dd66bbd39ae65499915a2","tid":747171,"uid":21481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係sleep apnea?"},{"pid":"90198d9e9bf24fa2fc2e9feb93e4de8a9552c37b","tid":747171,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"445c0d8aa11c0f618d5bb15d17eaa32c67f3d8ec","tid":747171,"uid":146066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:07:37.000Z","msg":"睡眠窒息症？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪<br />\n但我用過個app聽返<br />\n我個種鼻鼾聲係有規律 唔會突然停/超大聲<br />\n同埋上網睇又話關咽喉事所以側瞓可以令佢唔責住呼吸道 咁就唔會扯鼻鼾（甚至好多止鼻鼾產品都係針對仰睡添）<br />\n但<strong>我側瞓都會扯鼻鼾</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw<br />\n我會去睇醫生架<br />\n不過驚去私家淨睇已經好貴<br />\n政府又唔知要等幾耐"},{"pid":"c5b4456133b7529ee16c35a1c9e6527b31cbf862","tid":747171,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明冇擘大口但呢幾年先打鼻鼾"},{"pid":"f07b1c484b7a9e47da3f2094c4bf6b2095e89a7f","tid":747171,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b4456133b7529ee16c35a1c9e6527b31cbf862","tid":747171,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明冇擘大口但呢幾年先打鼻鼾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"想問巴打/絲打你係咪都有鼻敏感/夜晚訓教有鼻塞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係鼻敏感好勁 一晚要用好多紙巾<br />\n同埋近幾年大力咗呻鼻涕<br />\n唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9ad2f03d413cceb0af969389dc2848db64efd3","tid":747171,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f07b1c484b7a9e47da3f2094c4bf6b2095e89a7f","tid":747171,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b4456133b7529ee16c35a1c9e6527b31cbf862","tid":747171,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 